{"tid":676870,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖求幫拖)燈塔同名校secrets一樣正仆街 惡過共產黨","createTime":"2018-05-24T17:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T02:32:44.000Z","uid":113358,"like":177,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"80ba4076e89bdddade330f37bdc53f3db9e64dd4","tid":676870,"uid":113358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:24:54.000Z","msg":"話說我個fd今日係歪歪條宣傳片下面見到有個家長留言大屌遵理,<br />\n仲話andrew lo條柒頭去左日本吃渴玩樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 之後cap左張圖俾我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/011315_465457191f5f1cbcdc09f4de2b2d4c8f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F011315_465457191f5f1cbcdc09f4de2b2d4c8f.jpeg&h=65faf5e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得好仆街, 夜晚放左工打算留句言g持下個家長<br />\n順便睇下哈哈哈會唔會出黎道歉, <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/011340_3e90538182ba79fda2b784489e58f282.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F011340_3e90538182ba79fda2b784489e58f282.jpeg&h=b940ecfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知過一陣就俾人block左仲del埋我個留言<br />\n咁樣河蟹人地d comment真係火都黎<br />\n同名校secrets之前有咩分別牙?<br />\n<br />\n全能既連登仔有冇方法玩大佢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人誰無過, 但做錯野基本道句歉都係咁咦牙<br />\n個家長又講得好岩,<br />\n就黎報summer course班仔仔女女又準備俾燈塔昆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c948dfa1ed6224f137ea4eba1c9e8fb5df39aa15","tid":676870,"uid":26150,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:26:47.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1121758e5eebd1d5dae5c435f60ef890ed583b09","tid":676870,"uid":137840,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾學店 越做越差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e280ae2412e4c7ec1eb28b455a29617c4ae723","tid":676870,"uid":70415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1121758e5eebd1d5dae5c435f60ef890ed583b09","tid":676870,"uid":137840,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾學店 越做越差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:42:04.000Z","msg":"Richard走左最後就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a213935d2cb6bf32174e4705ddb526f90fa95e","tid":676870,"uid":76420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:43:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/no